solution: ```class Solution {
    public boolean digitCount(String num) {
        int n = num.length();
        int[] freq = new int[10];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int d = num.charAt(i) - '0';
            if (d < 10) freq[d]++;
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int expected = num.charAt(i) - '0';
            if (freq[i] != expected) return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
